to\n\t\t\t\timplement energy-saving or conservation measures pursuant to ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(iii)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Consideration"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H88507B127702403AB9A4AD282BC0D59C"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ", to enter into energy savings performance\n\t\t\t\tcontracts or utility energy service contracts equal to $1,000,000,000 in each\n\t\t\t\tyear during the 5-year period beginning on January 1, 2014.", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "paragraph (4)", "@value": "National Energy Conservation Policy Act/s:543/ss:f/p:4"}, "#text": "It shall be the goal of\n\t\t\t\tthe Federal Government, in the implementation of energy-saving or conservation\n\t\t\t\tmeasures pursuant to ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(iv)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Contracting\n\t\t\t\tgoal"}, "#text": "\n              ", "@id": "H386BF2A4C7E647E3908888F4BF7F30AD", "@commented": "no"}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": [{"#tail": ",\n\t\t\t\teach Federal agency shall submit to the ", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "clause (iv)", "@value": "National Energy Conservation Policy Act/s:543/ss:f/p:10/sp:C/cl:iv", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": " information regarding\n\t\t\t\tprogress made by the agency towards achieving the goal described in such\n\t\t\t\tclause. Not later than 60 days after each such September 30, the ", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "8900"}, {"#tail": ",\n\t\t\t\tacting through the Federal Energy Management Program, shall submit to the\n\t\t\t\t", "@entity-type": "federal-body", "#text": "Secretary", "@entity-id": "8900"}, {"#tail": " and the\n\t\t\t\t"